{"tid":2285035,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國12人涉嫌策劃襲擊清真寺被起訴","createTime":"2020-11-13T19:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T22:43:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"992c9c563cfab20043cfc8a71bfdb23e5c721a52","tid":2285035,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T19:10:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559935-20201113.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559935-20201113.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy1I2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=1d36b7d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559935-20201113.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2d8171ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559935-20201113.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n德國檢察部門落案起訴12名男子，指他們涉嫌對當地清真寺策劃武裝襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n檢察官的聲明表示，12名疑犯都是德國人，其中11人已被扣查、1人在逃，指他們定期會面策劃襲擊，部分人更承諾出資採購武器。<br />\n<br />\n德國近年發生多宗針對少數群體的襲擊。一名極端右翼分子去年在德國東部一座猶太會堂殺死2人。另外，一名極右支持者，涉嫌殺害一名呼籲支持難民的保守派政治人物，正面臨審訊。"},{"pid":"8a954ca80db9ff89a7f7a4627d5a650465deaced","tid":2285035,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T19:11:01.000Z","msg":"今次係極右"},{"pid":"d7cd5fb7e2fb3e2fd019ac1a29c0609c31d15b32","tid":2285035,"uid":65289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T19:32:40.000Z","msg":"香港警察水炮車射清真寺連道歉都唔使<br />\n邊個先係恐怖分子"},{"pid":"1e37cf626cc519f621f8dd4e096a196e384ceed8","tid":2285035,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T22:43:12.000Z","msg":"極左 vs 極右<br />\n<br />\n同一戰二戰前一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}